@NODE History "History"
@{u}History@{uu}

V1.0 - First version!

V1.1 - Fixed window opening (thanx Pietro!).
       Added Executive support & Task Information.
       Took 'are you sure?' requester off.
       Made the GUI font sensitive.
       Probably fixed the bug that selected nothingness task sometimes.
       Took path names out of the Process names so it looks nicer.
       
